        <description>Inconsolata is my first serious original font release. It is a monospace font, designed for code listings and the like, in print. There are a great many "programmer fonts," designed primarily for use on the screen, but in most cases do not have the attention to detail for high resolution rendering.
</description>
        <tags>font monospace inconsolata mono fixedWidth fixed</tags>
